{"tid":694983,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Halloween 月光光心慌慌2018最新預告","createTime":"2018-06-08T23:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T01:52:12.000Z","uid":175614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4906a5363b3fab70d960408591e667ab963492fc","tid":694983,"uid":175614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T23:53:11.000Z","msg":"Halloween係美國其中一套非常經典嘅恐怖片<br />\n可能香港人唔係太清楚，對猛鬼街同黑色星期五比較熟悉，但其實都係好出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次其實唔算係Reboot，而係繼1981年第二集後三十八年後嘅直接續集，仲搵嚟第一代女主角Jamie Lee Crutis做翻經典角色Laurie Strode。<br />\n當年套戲雖然成本低，但係因為氣氛營造得好，所以被視為經典之一。<br />\n希望今次新一集拍好啲，唔好好似啲Reboot恐怖片咁柒下柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ek1ePFp-nBI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fek1ePFp-nBI&d=e7AjZHL1bThJ9uGARpSsMJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4f2aa277\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ek1ePFp-nBI</a>"},{"pid":"7ed29146ec5ed76afe69813a683db6c4bfa66249","tid":694983,"uid":47864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T01:52:12.000Z","msg":"呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}